data.text: @AyaFubaraEneli @DrChristineMann Full support of all of this. And I trust that you will make a perfect path forward.

@DrChristineMann @heychey Yeah, my introversion has quadrupled for sure.  I’m definitely more intentional about who and what I give my energy. I want to go deeper rather than wider with my work. I’m also less inclined to let people use me for their selfish agendas.

@AyaFubaraEneli @heychey I’m an introvert by nature so in that regard it’s been ok. But the disappointment I feel in my fellow human beings is immense and I don’t see a way to get past it. That’s the challenge and daily struggle for me. 

You?
@DrChristineMann @heychey How are you adjusting to this new reality?    #
@karenhunter How are you handling it? I’m so quick to ask for a zoom link.
@AyaFubaraEneli Covid should not be a life-spoiler as it is a life-taker.
@AyaFubaraEneli 100% same. I keep seeing indoor unmasked photos of people I know who should know better. I have learned who I can truly count on, though.
